ismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pin1665703047845.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pin1665703047845.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pin1665703047845.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pin1665703047845\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Direction (Field Layout) </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Field layout property that specifies the text orientation of the field. </p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Shorthand Code</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__2\"> Representation </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LTR</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Left to right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use for most languages.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">RTL</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Right to left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pin1665703047845__table_d11249e1_d11250e1_d11251e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Use for languages such as Hebrew and Arabic.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pin1665703047845__p_d98597e1_d98598e1_d98599e1\">The value of this property overrides the assignment\n         setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$RTL_FIELDS</span>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pin1665703047845__section_a42_pf3_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1179090e150\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pin1665703047845__ul_zhd_qf3_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pin1665703047845__li_d3755e1_d3756e1_d3757e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ijx1665702711766.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ijx1665702711766.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Layout is a Development Object that defines the way data is displayed.\">Modeled Field Layout</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nvi1665702721301.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$RTL_FIELDS</a><p>Set the position of the cursor in the field at deployment. For right-to-left applications only.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615192\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615192\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Direction (Field Layout) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Direction (Field Layout) Field layout property that specifies the text orientation of the field. Shorthand Code Representation Description LTR Left to right Use for most languages. RTL Right to left Use for languages such as Hebrew and Arabic. The value of this property overrides the assignment setting $RTL_FIELDS . Applies to Modeled Field Layout Related Links $RTL_FIELDS Set the position of the cursor in the field at deployment. For right-to-left applications only. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}